[node name="RichTextLabel" type="RichTextLabel" parent="Layout/HBoxContainer/SectionTab/NewsContainer" unique_id=761584771]
layout_mode = 2
size_flags_vertical = 3
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[font_size=30]Beta 3[/font_size]
* [b]Log Reader Utility:[/b] Created a robust, multi-character log monitoring engine with intelligent day-rollover support and position tracking.
* [b]Moi Tracker:[/b] Fully implemented the \"Moment of Inspiration\" tracking suite.
    * [b]Team Management:[/b] Drag-and-drop team building with distinct Leader and Member roles.
    * [b]Team Presets:[/b] Save and load your crafting team configurations permanently.
    * [b]Modern UI:[/b] HTML-inspired responsive player cards with real-time stat tracking (MOIs, Crafts, CPM).
    * [b]Smart Timers:[/b] Interval-based crafting pacing with visual alerts and log-driven reset based on leader activity.
    * [b]Synchronization:[/b] Real-time global state syncing across multiple open tracker instances.
* [b]Player List Improvements:[/b] Enhanced the shared selection component with team-aware filtering and global update notifications.

[font_size=30]Beta 2[/font_size]
* [b]Player Editor:[/b] Implemented full directory management with Windows/Steam auto-discovery and character detection.
* [b]STP Calculator:[/b] Ported full skill difficulty database and math engine for precise skill tick simulations.
* [b]Affinity Food Planner:[/b] Re-engineered into a modern, fully reactive split-pane tool with advanced filtering for meat, cheese, salt, and herb stock exclusions.
* [b]Customer Database:[/b] Added a persistent database to track test meal results for external customers.
* [b]Reusable UI Components:[/b] Created vertical and horizontal player selection components for a consistent experience across all apps.
* [b]Data Persistence:[/b] Implemented secure JSON storage in the user directory for all paths, players, and customer data.

[font_size=30]Beta 1[/font_size]
* Added Main UI"

